The evidence with the title '5 reasons why fluoride in water is good for communities ' says Fluoride in water prevents dental disease, protects all ages against cavities,  ... An estimated 51 million school hours and 164 million work hours are lost each year  ... Cost per person to fluoridate a water supply is less than the cost of one dental filling. For most cities, every $1 invested in water fluoridation saves $38 in dental  ... 
